						               													<description>We Can Be Heroes II is a wargaming rule set for people who want fun games.  The rules have a focus on interactive lighthearted play, so don't bring your poker face to the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play is based around the adventures of heroes (or heroines) and their companions (Sidekicks), as they battle through one-off or linked scenarios.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Although intended for 25-28mm individual figures, the game will work with any scale of miniatures.  It is also very versatile and can recreate games at many levels from small skirmish to large scale battles with mutli-based miniatures in any period.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are rules to get you gaming a variety of periods from fantasy, sci-fi, WW2 &amp;amp; Vietnam.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;WCBH2 contains many helpful examples of play, guides, and thoughts on the application and spirit of the rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is suitable for solo or multiple players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Includes printable quick reference cards, character information and equipment cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
